<li>Your uncle will be deeply missed.  He was a wonderful man.</li>
<li>Sending love and strength your way.</li>
<li>So sorry for your loss.  May his memory be a blessing.</li>
<li>With heartfelt sympathy on the passing of your beloved uncle.</li>
<li>My thoughts and prayers are with you and your family.</li>
<li>I’m so saddened to hear about your uncle’s passing.</li>
<li>He'll be remembered fondly for his kindness and generosity.</li>
<li>Holding you close in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li>May the love you shared comfort you during this time.</li>
<li>Sending you all my love and support.</li>
<li>So very sorry to hear of your loss.  May he rest in peace.</li>
<li>I offer my deepest condolences to you and your family.</li>
<li>Please accept my sincere sympathy on the passing of your uncle.</li>
    

